body:
This PR ports most taskmanager related config parameters to config options.

The following keys were not ported as i wasn't sure whether they should really belong to the TaskManagerOptions.

```
DEFAULT_SPILLING_MAX_FAN_KEY = "taskmanager.runtime.max-fan";
DEFAULT_SORT_SPILLING_THRESHOLD_KEY = "taskmanager.runtime.sort-spilling-threshold";
RUNTIME_HASH_JOIN_BLOOM_FILTERS_KEY = "taskmanager.runtime.hashjoin-bloom-filters";
FS_STREAM_OPENING_TIMEOUT_KEY = "taskmanager.runtime.fs_timeout";
```

The PR contains 1 commit for each ported parameter.

The majority of changes are straight-forward.

Special attention should be given to `MAX_REGISTRATION_DURATION` in the `YarnResourceManager`.
The existing code parsed a timeunit String (i.e. "5 ms") directly as an integer via `Configuration#getInteger()`. This didn't make any sense to me, so i changed it to first create a `Duration`, convert it to seconds, and then create a `FiniteDuration` from it.
